admin.description: Returns the current admin of the contract.

changeAdmin.description: Changes the admin of the contract.

implementation.description: Returns the current implementation address of the contract.

upgradeTo.description: Upgrades the contract to a new implementation.

upgradeToAndCall.description: Upgrades the contract to a new implementation and makes a call to it.

fallback.description: Fallback function that allows the contract to receive Ether.

receive.description: Receive function to handle incoming Ether transfers.

AdminChanged.description: Emitted when the admin of the contract changes.

BeaconUpgraded.description: Emitted when the beacon address is upgraded.

Upgraded.description: Emitted when the implementation address is upgraded.
